{"tid":2286430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(抗爭手足) 王宗堯新戲《夜香．鴛鴦．深水埗》11月19日上映, 但上映戲院數目將不及吳京的反美國電影","createTime":"2020-11-15T04:09:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T17:46:59.000Z","uid":134071,"like":61,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f5fcc0f4f1a7e2afda39ad525b9372cd7aa5da","tid":2286430,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:09:51.000Z","msg":"Golden Scene發行,&nbsp; 抗爭手足 王宗堯有份主演(其中一個單元故事)的香港本土電影《夜香．鴛鴦．深水埗》 曾入圍國際知名既International Film Festival Rotterdam, 好威水.&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(電影故事細節上, 亦有一些令抗爭手足有共鳴既地方. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所以電檢處係電影開頭強加警告字句. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n而家, 《夜香．鴛鴦．深水埗》已定於11月19日在香港上映, 但據聞只會有約5間戲院上映,  開畫戲院數目將不及吳京的反美國電影《金剛川》 . <br />\n<br />\n《夜香．鴛鴦．深水埗》係非主流藝術片,&nbsp;開畫戲院數目數目少係可以理解.&nbsp;&nbsp;但好消息係上映戲院據悉應該包括UA K11 Art House和百老匯戲院中心.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>今次係黃藍電影第一次同期上映.  </strong>希望至少《夜香．鴛鴦．深水埗》入座率會高過《金剛川》. 戲院要人.  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS:&nbsp;&nbsp;另外,&nbsp;由日本撐港手足 水島努導演的《白箱:劇場版》(SHIROBAKO) 亦將於11月19日在香港上映.  水島努發聲支持香港示威者,&nbsp;&nbsp;令《白箱》被中共封殺.&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟會用多D時間推《夜香．鴛鴦．深水埗》, 但希望大家有時間都可以支持《白箱:劇場版》. <strong> 如果《夜香．鴛鴦．深水埗》和《白箱:劇場版》的入座率都超過《金剛川》, 絕對係振興黃圈.</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WZ356coOJZQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWZ356coOJZQ&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BHXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=d3ebd731\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WZ356coOJZQ</a>"},{"pid":"07f39a82bb1ec42b42ecf2a7995aa1afcda038bb","tid":2286430,"uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:10:34.000Z","msg":"畀中國封殺嘅「白箱」點解係黃圈電影？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2284405/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2284405/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"6321c363e547751afb3f179b5efa1ff7f352f1bc","tid":2286430,"uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:10:51.000Z","msg":"王宗堯係抗爭手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531290-20200610.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531290-20200610.htm&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BHXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=26a97b63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531290-20200610.htm&h=9466650c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531290-20200610.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8fbef97a2c2dd1aa4c51f67305104beb3ac45533","tid":2286430,"uid":232157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2a586d4acea0bb8b20db9012254f99c8f9a62e","tid":2286430,"uid":24345,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:15:17.000Z","msg":"又要搶飛"},{"pid":"745f5ef330f4a6c6621eee5f1060344f947763c8","tid":2286430,"uid":129042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:18:58.000Z","msg":"希望睇到"},{"pid":"1d30b233ca12ed63aa633f90092989640277e15e","tid":2286430,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fbef97a2c2dd1aa4c51f67305104beb3ac45533","tid":2286430,"uid":232157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets