edBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:04:34.000Z","msg":"四個關於香港人在回憶和現實之間蹓躂的故事：<br />\n<br />\n《出城記》<br />\n豉油、夜香、R啫啫：新舊老少兩個女移民結伴同行，企圖由元朗勇闖中環。<br />\n<br />\n《玩具故事》<br />\n貨Van、冼拿、卡碧煙：開朗內歛兩個兄弟一起尋寶，最後一次反轉母親經營的玩具店。<br />\n<br />\n《鴛鴦》<br />\n鴛鴦、炸雞、豬腸粉：本地經濟科及外籍英文科兩位中學教師食遍香港九龍新界，學期結束時為即將離港赴京的一方餞別。<br />\n<br />\n《It's not gonna be fun》<br />\n餵貓、拉花、企街站；最後，一位港女站起來，在深水埗為未來奮鬥參選區議會，挑戰建制，挑戰自己根本不愛deal with people的底線。"},{"pid":"bde99ef09d5be6d95b4a59a4d46a3629ab12415a","tid":2286430,"uid":232157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f75415d76068f1794254f8b8cab6e90df756be","tid":2286430,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bde99ef09d5be6d95b4a59a4d46a3629ab12415a","tid":2286430,"uid":232157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f344ed70e8f353969e6f7c065e9ae8483c879d8d","tid":2286430,"uid":260371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:15:26.000Z","msg":"百老匯電影中心有得睇，百老匯係黃確認無誤。"},{"pid":"73e35dc44bf073f22eefbcf8838ad38daa2a7221","tid":2286430,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f344ed70e8f353969e6f7c065e9ae8483c879d8d","tid":2286430,"uid":260371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:15:26.000Z","msg":"百老匯電